# BrainWave Fixer CAIAS

## Overview
BrainWave Fixer is an AI-powered educational tool that helps teachers identify which parts of a lesson students find difficult to understand.

Students can interact with study material, highlight confusing sections, and the system analyzes this data to improve teaching effectiveness.

---

## Features
- AI-generated study materials
- Confusion detection
- Quiz generation
- Progress tracking
- AI teacher assistance

---

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Run the app:
   python app.py

